ded. The distinguishing feature of this paper is\nthat the Young operators of conjugated Young diagrams are related by Clifford\nreversion, connecting Clifford algebra and Hecke algebra features. This\ncontrasts the purely Hecke algebraic approach of King and Wybourne, who do not\nembed Hecke algebras into Clifford algebras.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 1999 14:23:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
